title: Code Masters
description: October 22, 2020 - Code Masters was an online contest that tested the participants’ understanding of their lessons in IT111/IT111L (Concepts in Object Oriented Programming) and CS102-1/CS102-1L (Data Structures and Algorithms Analysis). It was executed using Kahoot! and it served as a review for their upcoming final exams.
summary: Code Masters was an online contest that tested the participants’ understanding of their lessons in IT111/IT111L and CS102-1/CS102-1L courses.
